resources.string:
NewtonLab application is an application that can record physics practicum activities and allows to calculate every action that has the consequence of causing a reaction. 

Newton's Law 3 reads, Every action will cause a reaction. If an object exerts a force on another object, the object that receives the force will exert a force equal to the force received from the first object, but in the opposite direction. 

This application was created to fulfill Assessment 2 - Mobpro 1.
